# Lacocina wordpress plugin

## Features

Currently two functions exists to support shortcodes:

`[githubissuescount]`
: number of (open) issues in github repository

  Required arguments:
  - `user`: your github user name
  - `project`: name of your github project
  - `issuelabel`: label of issue (ie 'bug)

`[commentscount]`
: number of comments in current blog message

## Installation

Installation takes place by copying this directory to:

* `/usr/share/wordpress/wp-content/plugins/lacocina-wordpress-plugin`

Development takes place in a git repository published on github:

* https://github.com/ronalde/lacocina-wordpress-plugin/

